title: De F*ckulteit
overview: Lawyer Anouk Boone becomes the youngest candidate partner ever at her firm. Soon, stories start circulating about how she achieved this position. During her studies, she had an affair with the flamboyant professor Hartman. When all kinds of complaints about Hartman's transgressive behavior surface in the storm of #MeToo, Anouk's memories of him take on a different meaning.
